        <updateDate>2019-10-30T15:49:50Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>American Data Dissemination Act of 2019 or the ADD Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Federal Trade Commission to recommend legislative action and propose regulations&nbsp;to impose&nbsp;privacy requirements on providers of internet services.</p> <p>Such regulations shall restrict a provider from disclosing a user's records, provide a user with the right to access and correct records maintained by a provider, establish practices for the collection and maintenance of records,&nbsp;and exempt certain small providers from the regulations' requirements. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
